title: Soul Liquid Chambers
original_name: ソウルリキッドチェインバーズ
sinopse:
A girl with prosthetic limbs and a tragic past wanders a zombie-ridden 23rd century earth now known as Dead Man's Playground. Overrun by monsters, the post-apocalyptic wasteland is the last place a little girl should call home, but she's developed a unique coping mechanism...

(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)
